headline: Aetherflux Appoints Joe Yaffe as Chief Operating Officer and Chief Legal Officer
summary: Aetherflux, the space-based solar power company founded by Robinhood co-founder Baiju Bhatt, today announced the appointment of Joe Yaffe as Chief Operating Officer (COO) and Chief Legal Officer (CLO). In this dual executive role, Yaffe will oversee the company's worldwide operations, legal, and regulatory affairs.
